integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
