STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2338:research/history/logs/agent_round_0040_repair_1.stdout.log:6079:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u6b21 repair \u6ca1\u6709\u6539 family_name\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6539 env_overrides\uff1b\u4ecd\u7136\u662f\u76f8\u5bf9 r27 \u53ea\u5207\u6362\u5230 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002\u963b\u585e\u6839\u56e0\u662f `Unknown architecture`\uff0c\u5df2\u6309\u67b6\u6784\u96c6\u6210 checklist \u4fee\u590d\uff1awhitelist\u3001dispatch\u3001class\u3001exact-string smoke \u90fd\u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u3002\u989d\u5916\u628a\u8be5 family \u63a5\u5230\u4e86 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u540e\u7eed\u8c03\u53c2\u65f6\u9759\u9ed8\u5931\u6548\u3002exact smoke \u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` \u4e0a\u901a\u8fc7\uff0c\u4f30\u7b97\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7ea6 1.06x \u539f\u59cb matmul\u3001\u9884\u7b97\u6bd4\u7387 0.71x\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u5185\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2345:research/history/logs/agent_round_0039.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":37,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_total_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做 sparse cleanup，因此仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r37 已在 K=192、EF=1 下得到强质量锚点 FVU≈0.0424；本轮相对 r37 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK: 384 -> 128`，主假设是当前 trunk 明显过重，降低 trunk rank 后仍能保留大部分重构质量，同时把 total_cost 从约 1.06x 压到约 0.69x，从而把这条新结构性前沿往低到中成本带延伸。","summary":"以 r37 的强质量结果为参考，只下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，测试 `lowrank_expert_residual` 能否在明显更低 total_cost 下保持接近 r37 的低 FVU。这比继续在高成本点附近微调更符合当前低开销探索目标。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r37 只修改 `TRUNK_RANK`。该改动同时降低 encoder 与 deployment 成本，归因清晰，且直接回答当前最关键的问题：这条新 family 是否能形成一段向低中成本延展的 Pareto 段。相比继续调 `STAGE1_RATIO`，`TRUNK_RANK` 更契合 Round 39 的低成本优先策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 仍保持明显优于现有 <0.8x 区域 anchor 的 FVU，则下一轮继续保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，细化这条新 Pareto 段的形状。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 FVU 退化过大，则说明该 family 的质量对 trunk 依赖较强；下一轮优先回到同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 寻找折中点。","如果该 family 在降成本后仍具竞争力，则 `two-stage residual expert` 的优先级可以暂时后移，因为当前 family 已经回答了三段式结构值得继续。"],"notes_to_memory":["r37 `lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1` 已产生强质量锚点，val_fvu≈0.042385。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前实现的成本估算，`TRUNK_RANK=128` 时 combined_ratio≈0.69x，显著低于 r37 的≈1.06x，且仍在硬约束内。","Round 39 应优先回答这条新 family 是否能向低中成本带延展，而不是回到 plain selector 家族继续扫 K。"],"touched_files":[]}
